                "id": "dock_read",
                "kind": "visit_room",
                "text": "The civilian shipyard boards list which berth is pretending to be empty. Walk the lane and confirm the posted arrival story.",
                "roomKeysAny": [
                    "Meridian Civil Shipyard"
