            {
                "id": "glyph_finale",
                "kind": "choice",
                "prompt": "You can hand security a clean chain-of-custody note that burns Mira\u2019s upstream forgeries \u2014 or sell the forged seal pattern to the first broker who pays before the sweep lands.",
